    <item>
      <title>EQen 1.9.6</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 22:48:44 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>EQen.16</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.9.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[Compact horizontal meter strip replaces the 4-column tower — ~3x less vertical space, with pause + hide toggles. EasyEffects import now pulls compressor and limiter settings, not just EQ bands; warning dialog rewritten to be honest about what actually doesn't map.]]></description>
