    <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.9.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
    <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
    <description><![CDATA[UI overhaul: new design system (dark-first with cyan accent), interactive EQ curve plot with draggable band dots as the main control surface, redesigned Effects window with category-coloured cards, polished menu bar popover, integrated top-bar chrome.]]></description>
